{"tid":940551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警超聯】男警涉呃學資處19.3萬　明年2月開審","createTime":"2018-12-14T04:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T20:49:37.000Z","uid":54337,"like":144,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9768853f4e9ba3a5c18456cdfa2afa534acc43","tid":940551,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:26:46.000Z","msg":"男警涉呃學資處19.3萬　明年2月開審<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/jiCCggi3RqMHS/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FjiCCggi3RqMHS%2Fgiphy.gif&h=4f4f6763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年輕男警員被指於5年前向學生資助辦事處(現稱學生資助處)申請資助時，涉嫌隱瞞財務狀況，詐騙學資處逾19.3萬港元。男警被控兩項欺詐罪，今(14日)在西九龍法院否認控罪，案件定於明年2月18日開審，預計需時兩天。<br />\n<br />\n被告古俊輝，現年26歲，控罪指被告於2013年9月至2014年3月間，以及2014年5月至12月間，在香港藉欺騙向學生資助辦事處虛報或漏報他或他家人沒擁有土地或物業，意圖詐騙而誘使學資處根據專上學生資助計劃，分別向他發放約9.39萬港元及9.94萬港元的款項，兩筆款項合共約19.3萬港元，因而導致他本人獲益，或導致學資處蒙受不利或相當可能蒙受不利。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181214/mobile/bkn-20181214120051770-1214_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181214%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181214120051770-1214_00822_001.html&d=m2Npfn1q63F%2F9P%2BwYsCmZ%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=50656e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181214/mobile/bkn-20181214120051770-1214_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7e811ff76d77618cf9e834d791ba228a69d31810","tid":940551,"uid":54337,"like":60,"dislike":0,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181214/photo/bkn-20181214120051770-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181214121530\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181214120051770-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181214121530&h=b55a7bfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12e7aac17c75c6109bbf554608d745d260f0de02","tid":940551,"uid":87780,"like":156,"dislike":1,"sco